summary:
- **All resolutions passed** at Firetail Resources' General Meeting (31/07/2025), including:  
  - Ratification of prior share issuance (99.97% approval).  
  - Director participation in placement (Glenn Poole, Simon Lawson, Robert Jewson - all ~99.98% approval).  
  - Issuance of options to Joint Lead Managers (99.98% approval).  
  - **Company name change** (99.98% approval).  
  - Share issuance for acquisitions:  
    - Excelsior Project (99.98% approval).  
    - Bella Project (99.98% approval).  
  - Issuance of ZEPOs to directors (~99.8% approval).  

*No material trading or capital structure impacts identified beyond routine approvals.*
